{"tid":2299679,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"「國安法下無人安全」陳日君勸移民","createTime":"2020-11-25T03:26:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-25T04:46:11.000Z","uid":25558,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3bbf6ac970026f94ddf743543bd85097438c1e12","tid":2299679,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:26:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/U7VIX4OKUJGP5GU55YZLSRYC74/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FU7VIX4OKUJGP5GU55YZLSRYC74%2F&d=oTNoRcAbgn%2B4rVu%2B4XO%2FKOvO%2FPyVe1I8S2KINgfvOuE%3D&h=191da4ae\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201125%2FU7VIX4OKUJGP5GU55YZLSRYC74%2F&h=fe0907b0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201125/U7VIX4OKUJGP5GU55YZLSRYC74/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n「國安法下無人安全」陳日君勸移民<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/KI360RvZHlgyZtunanEls6Kt4SM=/720x461/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/SEMTRZJ3H5E3HFH7IJBVBDNNLQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FKI360RvZHlgyZtunanEls6Kt4SM%3D%2F720x461%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FSEMTRZJ3H5E3HFH7IJBVBDNNLQ.jpg&h=9d5c05a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■陳日君受訪形容港人在國安法下已「失去了一切」。資料圖片<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】天主教香港教區榮休主教陳日君樞機雖然已退休，。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n由跨國獨立記者組成的WION昨發表陳日君樞機的專訪，。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n他形容國安法「可怕」、「。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n斥京梵協議加劇迫害教徒<br />\n<br />\n陳日君亦留意到近期移民潮，「突然間，甚至有許多勇敢的人說他們想離開香港，有些人卻害怕說任何話，因為這可能會造成破壞，看似一切都結束了，而我們真的處於最低谷」。<br />\n<br />\n陳日君鼓勵港人在有能力的情況下離開香港，特別是有子女的人，因為教育已被用作洗腦，目前情況已達非常危險的地步。<br />\n<br />\n面對近期政府連番對教育界施壓，他認為在國安法下最受威脅的正是教育界，政府不尊重教師，即使校方曾表明老師們無做錯任何事，仍一意孤行取消教師資格。他希望全世界能注意到香港局勢變化，並鼓勵中國政府變得更明智。<br />\n<br />\n陳。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n記者問陳日君為何會覺得梵蒂岡與中國的交易會損害中國的天主教徒，他說協議只是讓中國政府可以迫害教會的藉口，「有時他們說壞協議總比無協議好，這是無法理解的，因為壞事就是壞事。 您可能接受不完善的協議，但不能接受不正確的協議。」"},{"pid":"2bcfde27ca050a70803bf856be2daee567bfe940","tid":2299679,"uid":231480,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:27:54.000Z","msg":"陳樞機<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n雖然佢大愛和理非"},{"pid":"eaa72b2af288f5955587ffed694506edafa34179","tid":2299679,"uid":51752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:29:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lihkg/smile_hb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90b608242b07bd860ea8169057541f0c862a088e","tid":2299679,"uid":155095,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:30:51.000Z","msg":"佢老細都奶埋共，心淡啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pic7.dwnews.net/20190318/a8af9ddab7ea5dca46a3d7c9650ab073_w.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpic7.dwnews.net%2F20190318%2Fa8af9ddab7ea5dca46a3d7c9650ab073_w.jpg&h=64b71990&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"901efaa913050c6a052caa4d83e54828f7eaffef","tid":2299679,"uid":140967,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n<br />\n點解陳日君唔叫神出黎幫手救港人？主教黎架"},{"pid":"83d75a4b8b1c4ad3862f6c611fa354003d6d5097","tid":2299679,"uid":366470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"901efaa913050c6a052caa4d83e54828f7eaffef","tid":2299679,"uid":140967,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:32:01.000Z","msg":"下<br />\n<br />\n點解陳日君唔叫神出黎幫手救港人？主教黎架"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-25T03:33:26.000Z","msg":"因為最大嗰個教宗都奶埋共<br />\n神都拯救唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5df69bc1d9e62875460ee3ec2c6849a352506996","tid":2299679,"uid":155095,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"901efaa913050c6a052caa4d83e54828f7eaffef","tid":2299679,"ui